It took me around six years to realize that feeling intimidated was the primary reason for not contributing code to Open Source projects.

Even if I don't have strong programming experience or I master a programming language, I could do it. I could contribute.

&nbsp;

When was the last time you created some/any content?

We consume Gigabytes of content every day but how much do we produce? When was the last time you checked your instagram's, facebook's or any other social media network data consumption?

